{
  "stem": "15577.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thousands who, who-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] were with us, were sent to two or three or four camps in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- nobody stayed in, in Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And part of them perished-- until the end of the war, and it wasn't with us, after the war, part was saved, and most of them took place in-- took a part in this very famous death-- march to death.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were sent to-- we got a, a full bread, everybody of us, which, which nobody of us saw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A very long period of time-- one bread for one person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which afterwards, we understood it because it took a long time to go to there, although the distance was not too-- too- too big.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we went-- we, we got water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody got a bottle of water or something like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we came-- we came to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Schlindler awaited us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- there was a, a textile factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were brought, brought to this textile factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Afterwards, we knew that this factory was belonging to Jews before the war and was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] taken over by Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And now, we were living in the same factory, in second and third floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a complex of buildings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a very big factory, very well known.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Afterwards, we laughed about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think the name of the owner was Behr or something like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The first thing we had to do is to, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to take out the machines of the textile factory, to put them away, and to put in their places the munition machines, the special machines.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
